query:
insert into nft_auction (
            address, 
            root,
            nft,
            collection,
            tx_lt,
            nft_owner,
            status
        )
        select 
            unnest($1::varchar[]),
            unnest($2::varchar[]),
            unnest($3::varchar[]),
            unnest($4::varchar[]),
            unnest($5::bigint[]),
            unnest($6::varchar[]),
            $7::auction_status
        on conflict(address) do nothing
